news.title: Apple fights $27.5 mln legal fee request in California class action - Reuters
news.description: Apple Inc has asked a judge to reject a request for $27.5 million in legal fees from a law firm that represented plaintiffs in a $95 million settlement of a consumer class action lawsuit alleging deceptive AppleCare warranty practices.
